"title": "6650: finding",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6650: finding",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Discovering something or someone that is being looked for. The whole of Scripture points to God seeking out lost human beings and finding them. The delight of people at finding things (such as lost coins or wayward sons) is seen as a parable of the joy of God over repentant sinners.</p>\n<h2>Finding by searching</h2>\n<h3>People do not always find what they are searching for</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:6\">PRO 20:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:36-Gen27:40\">GEN 27:36–27:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:20\">2SA 17:20</a></p>\n<h3>God is sometimes found without being sought</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:20\">ROM 10:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:1\">ISA 65:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:30-Rom9:31\">ROM 9:30–9:31</a></p>\n<h2>Promises that God can be found</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:29\">DEU 4:29</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:8\">MAT 7:7–7:8</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:10\">LUK 11:9–11:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:13-Jer29:14\">JER 29:13–29:14</a></p>\n<h2>People's joy in finding God</h2>\n<h3>Finding the kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:44\">MAT 13:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:45-Matt13:46\">MAT 13:45–13:46</a></p>\n<h3>Finding the infant Jesus</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:9-Matt2:11\">MAT 2:9–2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:10-Luke2:12\">LUK 2:10–2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:16-Luke2:18\">LUK 2:16–2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Finding the Messiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:41\">JHN 1:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:36\">MRK 1:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:45\">JHN 1:45</a></p>\n<h3>Finding the risen Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:20\">JHN 20:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:1-Matt28:9\">MAT 28:1–28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:40-Luke24:43\">LUK 24:40–24:43</a></p>\n<h2>Results of finding God</h2>\n<h3>Finding truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:31-John8:32\">JHN 8:31–8:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:4-Ps25:5\">PSA 25:4–25:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:3-1Tim2:4\">1TI 2:3–2:4</a></p>\n<h3>Finding rest and security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:7\">PSA 36:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:4\">PSA 91:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:29\">MAT 11:28–11:29</a></p>\n<h3>Finding mercy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:13\">PRO 28:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:9\">PSA 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:7\">MAT 5:7</a></p>\n<h3>Finding satisfaction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:24-Eccl2:25\">ECC 2:24–2:25</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Finding success</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:14\">1SA 18:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:23\">GEN 39:23</a></p>\n<h3>Finding life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:35\">PRO 8:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:13-Matt7:14\">MAT 7:13–7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:39\">MAT 10:39</a></p>\n<h2>God's joy in finding repentant sinners</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:3-Luke15:7\">LUK 15:3–15:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:8-Luke15:32\">LUK 15:8–15:32</a></p>\n<h2>Other aspects of finding in life</h2>\n<h3>Finding things</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:21\">DEU 14:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:24-Matt17:27\">MAT 17:24–17:27</a></p>\n<h3>Finding people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:38\">GEN 41:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:1\">ACT 19:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:16-2Tim1:17\">2TI 1:16–1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Finding a wife</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:1-Gen24:4\">GEN 24:1–24:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:22\">PRO 18:22</a></p>\n<h3>Finding wisdom</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13\">PRO 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:14\">PRO 24:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">JAS 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>Finding God's will</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num9:8\">NUM 9:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:17\">JHN 7:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a></p>\n<h3>Sin finds people out</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:23\">NUM 32:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:1-2Sam12:14\">2SA 12:1–12:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:1-Acts5:11\">ACT 5:1–5:11</a></p>",
